#еҹәзЎҖsqlиҜӯеҸҘгҖҒи§ҶеӣҫгҖҒзәҰжқҹгҖҒзҙўеј•гҖҒеҮҪж•°еөҢеҘ—
drop table t1;
create table t1 as select des_encrypt('test','key') as c2;
alter table t1 add c1 int first;
alter table t1 modify c1 int auto_increment primary key;
desc t1;
+-------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field | Type          | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+-------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| c1    | int(11)       | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| c2    | varbinary(25) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
+-------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
insert into t1(c2) values(des_encrypt('222','key'));
insert into t1(c2) values(des_encrypt('333','key'));
insert into t1(c2) values(des_encrypt('444','key'));
select * from t1;
+----+-----------+
| c1 | c2        |
+----+-----------+
|  1 | я6өЧiа–!      |
|  2 | я.ҖјҡуҠDҗ        |
|  3 | яһ¶М3}ҳЗ       |
|  4 | я?ӢPҘБK;     |
+----+-----------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') from t1;
+----+-----------------------+
| c1 | des_decrypt(c2,'key') |
+----+-----------------------+
|  1 | test                  |
|  2 | 222                   |
|  3 | 333                   |
|  4 | 444                   |
+----+-----------------------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 where c1 = 1 group by c1,'key';
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  1 | test |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 where c1 = 2 order by 1;
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  2 | 222  |
+----+------+
select des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 where c1 = 3 order by 1 limit 1;
+------+
| key  |
+------+
| 333  |
+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 tt1 where exists(select * from t1 tt2 where tt2.c1 = tt1.c1 and tt2.c1 <= 1);
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  1 | test |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 tt1 where not exists(select * from t1 tt2 where tt2.c1 = tt1.c1 and tt2.c1 <= 1);
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  2 | 222  |
|  3 | 333  |
|  4 | 444  |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 where des_decrypt(c2,'key') in('test','333');
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  1 | test |
|  3 | 333  |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 where des_decrypt(c2,'key') not in('test','333');
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  2 | 222  |
|  4 | 444  |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 tt1 where c1 < any(select c1 from t1 tt2 where tt2.c1 > 2);
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  1 | test |
|  2 | 222  |
|  3 | 333  |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 tt1 where c1 = some(select c1 from t1 tt2 where tt2.c1 > 2);
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  3 | 333  |
|  4 | 444  |
+----+------+
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as 'key' from t1 tt1 where c1 > all(select c1 from t1 tt2 where tt2.c1 < 2);
+----+------+
| c1 | key  |
+----+------+
|  2 | 222  |
|  3 | 333  |
|  4 | 444  |
+----+------+
update t1 set c2 = des_encrypt('111','key') where des_decrypt(c2,'key') = 'test';
delete from t1 where des_decrypt(c2,'key') > des_decrypt(des_encrypt(111,'111'),'111');
select c1,des_decrypt(c2,'key') as new_c2 from t1;
+----+--------+
| c1 | new_c2 |
+----+--------+
|  1 | 111    |
+----+--------+
